The large kitchen features ample cabinetry, slate flooring, stainless appliances, and concealed laundry, and opens to a wonderful family room, which steps down to the sunny rear deck. The home also features a huge undeveloped attic with three skylights and a height of approximately 10 feet at the peak, while the large basement offers additional expansion potential. The rear cottage offers an updated full kitchen, dining area and laundry on the lower level, and a large living room, bedroom and remodeled bath upstairs, with fantastic east bay and downtown views. Because it`s fully detached, the cottage is the perfect rental unit, or a great family space or au pair/in-law apartment. There is two-car parking in the rear, accessed by Nellie Alley. 	Elegant residence located in prestigious gated community Deer Creek. This home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac, features 3,063 SF. 4 Bed, 3 Bath, and 3 Car Garage. Impressive curb appeal, stone detailed facade, front yard meticulously landscaped. Offering formal living & dining rooms, detailed by crown molding w/hardwood floors which accentuate their elegance. Gourmet kitchen w/granite countertops, island, maple cabinets, walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances, high bar & a breakfast nook w/ mitered glass that allow unobstructed views of pool area. Among upgrades you'll find Brazilian cherry hardwood floors in common areas, double tray ceilings in formal dining and in master bed, stunning columns throughout. Open, spacious family room displays a built in wall to wall entertainment center, volume windows & sliding doors to lanai. Expansive owner's retreat w/sitting area, slider door to lanai, 2 x-large walk-in closets, spa feel master bath: Jacuzzi tub, glass-enclosed shower, dual vanities & corian counters. Expansive screened lanai w/heated spa & pool w/saline system. New upgraded carpet & California closets in secondary bedrms. High efficiency A/C. Alarm system w/motion & glass break detectors. beautifully proportioned and sunny home is located high above the city in the new Robert A.M. Stern designed Brompton full service condominium on East 85th Street. Offering a spacious 2,567sf layout with 4 bedrooms, each with their own bath ensuite, plus a powder room. A wide and gracious entry foyer leads to a 33' south facing double living room with herringbone wood floors and open south views, a dining room and top of the line kitchen with a separate breakfast area. The master bedroom includes two walk-in closets and a spa bath with tub, stall shower and double sinks. The separate fourth bedroom works perfectly as a guest suite or office/library with custom built-in bookshelves. This elegantly appointed home has multi-zoned air conditioning, tremendous storage including a walk-in 50sf storage room, a laundry room and is wired for sound. The Brompton is a fulltime doorman and concierge condominium with a large gym, entertaining room with kitchen, children's playroom and planted and furnished sun deck. Additional Equinox gym is around the corner. 421-A tax abatement in place. :: 104 :: Less :: 105 :: javascript:void(0); :: 106 :: This beautifully proportioned and sunny home is located high above the city in the new Robert A.M. Sponsored Search. Sponsored Search offers an effective way to connect with customers searching for your products and services. This program uses a performance-based model in which businesses bid for enhanced placement in search results on terms that are relevant to their business, and pay on a per-click basis. Sponsor Results only appear when they're relevant to the specific searches.
